Package xbrlcore.xlink

Class Summary
Arc This class represents an arc in a linkbase file.
ExtendedLinkElement This class is an abstract super class for possible extended link elements, namely locators and resources.
Locator This class represents a locator within a linkbase.

A locator can either refer to a concept of a taxonomy or to a resource within another linkbase.
Resource This class represents a resource within a linkbase.
